---
scenario: >-
  As part of an online service, you are provided a page to check the records you've previously entered, add more or continue with the service. Things to try:

  1. You would like to change your answer for one of the questions for one of the records.
  
  2. You would like to delete a record

  3. You would like to add a new record

notes: The links to change your answers are not functional.
---

